" data-hidetabletportrait="1" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-luZMM6lh0ptQ-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-FSFHeNhWv4V9" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-FSFHeNhWv4V9-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-uthD2lg5Sbak" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-uthD2lg5Sbak-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-OhYZen2vppwU" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-OhYZen2vppwU-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-DqHJ6A0AsCwB n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item5" class="n2-font-321dc5071321283da51868cafdcfd437-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:inline-block;">Signature d’un accord de double diplôme avec l’Université Française d’Egypte (UFE)</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-L5PIttazLFpo" data-pm="default" role="button" onclick="n2ss.applyActionWithClick(event, 'next');" data-href="#" tabindex="0" data-force-pointer="" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-L5PIttazLFpo-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-FGDnvBPHlW6r n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><span class="n2i  n2-ss-851item6 nfa nfa-long-arrow-right n2-ss-item-content" style="font-size:156.25%;"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-slide-duration="0" data-id="4054" data-slide-public-id="2" data-title="Ergoskel" class="n2-ss-slide n2-ow  n2-ss-slide-4054"><div role="note" class="n2-ss-slide--focus" tabindex="-1">Ergoskel</div><div class="n2-ss-layers-container n2-ss-slide-limiter n2-ow"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-JQrIKLtDKva4" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-3JAYJx8TJTn7" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-3JAYJx8TJTn7-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n2-ss-stretch-layer n-uc-1lrRB1dkQF7H" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-1lrRB1dkQF7H-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-YaeSYHLnmMf2" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-YaeSYHLnmMf2-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-kR2cF91X0SuZ" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item7" class="n2-font-cd8573d8a507c95a4dc96d2cf74b8d59-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;"> L’UTC, là où l’innovation protège la santé au travail </div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-7etxowMCJ4ob" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d59dca73119e9ed568f3684d94eea568-paragraph   ">Savez-vous que l’ErgoSkel, un exosquelette léger qui aide les préparateurs et préparatrices de commandes à réduire la fatigue musculaire, a été développé à l’UTC ? C’est Khalil Ben Mansour, enseignant-chercheur à l’UTC, responsable de la plateforme d’analyse du mouvement, qui a conçu cette innovation brevetée en collaboration avec FM Logistic, avec le concours de la SATT Lutech. Il s'agit d'un dispositif ergonomique et non motorisé qui accompagne les mouvements du dos et des bras pour diminuer les efforts physiques lors du port de charges répétées. Les personnes utilisant cet exosquelette présentent donc moins de troubles musculosquelettiques et plus de confort pour la manipulation de colis lourds ! </p>
</div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-glDbWkXT8f3q n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-click="n2ss.trigger(e.currentTarget, 'details');" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-button-container n2-ss-item-content n2-ow n2-font-b6843e460493f4d2e4f47b6d9745514d-link  n2-ss-nowrap n2-ss-button-container--non-full-width"><a class="n2-style-c6c5507bd4502a08633174b84f534e5b-heading  n2-ow " target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hWBv_kLT-eo"><div><div>Voir la vidéo</div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-ecfgF8KkSSXY" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-ecfgF8KkSSXY-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-DPBrJyslFEvY" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item10" class="n2_ss_video_player n2-ss-item-content n2-ow-all" data-aspect-ratio="16:9"><div class="n2_ss_video_player__placeholder" ></div><div id="n2-ss-851item10-frame"></div><div class="n2_ss_video_player__cover" data-force-pointer=""><picture class="n2-ow-all skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><source srcset="//www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/slider/cache/703086f0e0008500e4843edfc8c906bf/hqdefault.webp" type="image/webp" media="(max-width: 200px)" class="skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><source srcset="//www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/slider/cache/8e272a093ee66fcfd86e899421f5fe1d/hqdefault.webp" type="image/webp" class="skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><img class="n2_ss_video_cover skip-lazy" alt="Lecture" loading="lazy" width="480" height="360" data-skip-lazy="1" src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hWBv_kLT-eo/hqdefault.jpg" /></picture><img class="n2_ss_video_play_btn skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1" width="48" height="48" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Play"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-TOqJm3oIB9m0" data-pm="normal" data-hidedesktopportrait="1" data-hidetabletportrait="1" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-TOqJm3oIB9m0-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-ruXobgIIqjRY" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-ruXobgIIqjRY-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-OU8WTikutS8a" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-OU8WTikutS8a-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-Rat1XIEU4mw1" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-Rat1XIEU4mw1-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-IfZpfn8pKUOv n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item11" class="n2-font-321dc5071321283da51868cafdcfd437-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:inline-block;">Signature d’un accord de double diplôme avec l’Université Française d’Egypte (UFE)</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-9uIpcZARM2rc" data-pm="default" role="button" onclick="n2ss.applyActionWithClick(event, 'next');" data-href="#" tabindex="0" data-force-pointer="" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-9uIpcZARM2rc-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-Mg74yrN1Fhv6 n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><span class="n2i  n2-ss-851item12 nfa nfa-long-arrow-right n2-ss-item-content" style="font-size:156.25%;"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-slide-duration="0" data-id="4023" data-slide-public-id="3" data-title="66" class="n2-ss-slide n2-ow  n2-ss-slide-4023"><div role="note" class="n2-ss-slide--focus" tabindex="-1">66</div><div class="n2-ss-layers-container n2-ss-slide-limiter n2-ow"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-oFIanKsowMti" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-9aiMdcOVuxTS" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-9aiMdcOVuxTS-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n2-ss-stretch-layer n-uc-kbpoulUxpGFa" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-kbpoulUxpGFa-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-fNwPG9sr3WAi" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-fNwPG9sr3WAi-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-4W8BvWt1F7Tp n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item13" class="n2-font-a0801e962196f92af10770cb13115e64-hover n2-style-586043f04afba270c9d0bd72659a1aef-heading   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:inline-block;">DOSSIER</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-unPw4GbR2I1V" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item14" class="n2-font-cd8573d8a507c95a4dc96d2cf74b8d59-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">Performances et durabilité des batteries</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-Cd9cyYVoD4g7" data-pm="normal" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d59dca73119e9ed568f3684d94eea568-paragraph   ">Les impératifs tant de la transition énergétique que du souci de souveraineté guident un grand nombre des recherches menées à l’UTC. Ainsi, avec l’essor de l’électromobilité, les batteries sont au cœur de nombre de thématiques, notamment au sein des laboratoires Roberval et Avenues. Des problématiques tels, entre autres, le vieillissement des batteries, leur durabilité et performances, ou encore leur réutilisation sont développées. L’UTC a ainsi proposé des solutions pour la recharge en quelques minutes, pour une sécurité accrue, mais aussi pour mieux comprendre le fonctionnement de la batterie vis-à-vis de son environnement. Ces travaux bénéficient aux intégrateurs de batteries (automobile, aéronautique, ferroviaire, réseaux…) et à leurs fabricants. C’est notamment le cas pour le développement des batteries sodium-ion, une technologie qui permettrait de s’affranchir de matériaux critiques.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-5P0k5dCbmcSo n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-click="n2ss.trigger(e.currentTarget, 'details');" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-button-container n2-ss-item-content n2-ow n2-font-b6843e460493f4d2e4f47b6d9745514d-link  n2-ss-nowrap n2-ss-button-container--non-full-width"><a class="n2-style-c6c5507bd4502a08633174b84f534e5b-heading  n2-ow " target="_blank" href="https://interactions.utc.fr/thematiques/design-industriel/66-performances-et-durabilite-des-batteries/"><div><div>Lire le dossier</div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-ONGPXmWmHOvK" data-pm="normal" data-hidedesktopportrait="1" data-hidetabletportrait="1" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-ONGPXmWmHOvK-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-RoWaLKAJdbH2" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-RoWaLKAJdbH2-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-vDENo5I8oHlm" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-vDENo5I8oHlm-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-t0A3EZKEClg6" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-t0A3EZKEClg6-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-GNeASPQWPByI n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item17" class="n2-font-321dc5071321283da51868cafdcfd437-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:inline-block;">Impression moléculaire : une technologie de pointe</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-H4I79Rb5XPkU" data-pm="default" role="button" onclick=