cofondateur de la startup EPPUR, conçoit des solutions innovantes pour améliorer le quotidien des personnes en fauteuil roulant grâce à un système de freinage révolutionnaire.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-ogJiSVxyCtYV n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-click="n2ss.trigger(e.currentTarget, 'details');" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-button-container n2-ss-item-content n2-ow n2-font-b6843e460493f4d2e4f47b6d9745514d-link  n2-ss-nowrap n2-ss-button-container--non-full-width"><a class="n2-style-c6c5507bd4502a08633174b84f534e5b-heading  n2-ow " target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/live/TS9vQrBRMhc?feature=shared"><div><div>Voir la vidéo</div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-LKeQqkX3qMr9" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-LKeQqkX3qMr9-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-ZMtbYEEMukYH" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item28" class="n2_ss_video_player n2-ss-item-content n2-ow-all" data-aspect-ratio="16:9"><div class="n2_ss_video_player__placeholder" ></div><div id="n2-ss-851item28-frame"></div><div class="n2_ss_video_player__cover" data-force-pointer=""><picture class="n2-ow-all skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><source srcset="//www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/slider/cache/d3cf45b3d5d3f524f06551e64a48239f/hqdefault.webp" type="image/webp" media="(max-width: 200px)" class="skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><source srcset="//www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/slider/cache/ffbd5e69a8813ce7883dfa5832e9ad3a/hqdefault.webp" type="image/webp" class="skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><img class="n2_ss_video_cover skip-lazy" alt="Lecture" loading="lazy" width="480" height="360" data-skip-lazy="1" src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/TS9vQrBRMhc/hqdefault.jpg" /></picture><img class="n2_ss_video_play_btn skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1" width="48" height="48" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Play"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-XzVh6dSTinWD" data-pm="normal" data-hidedesktopportrait="1" data-hidetabletportrait="1" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-XzVh6dSTinWD-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-Ck9g1KfzM9Nk" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-Ck9g1KfzM9Nk-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-hxcPx0xCCCHq" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-hxcPx0xCCCHq-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-y7cFBzUBWTkO" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-y7cFBzUBWTkO-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-sz0c0wboGefN n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item29" class="n2-font-321dc5071321283da51868cafdcfd437-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:inline-block;">Signature d’un accord de double diplôme avec l’Université Française d’Egypte (UFE)</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-3STbZD6BOca4" data-pm="default" role="button" onclick="n2ss.applyActionWithClick(event, 'next');" data-href="#" tabindex="0" data-force-pointer="" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-3STbZD6BOca4-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-DIMaNYYaCLe4 n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><span class="n2i  n2-ss-851item30 nfa nfa-long-arrow-right n2-ss-item-content" style="font-size:156.25%;"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-slide-duration="0" data-id="4096" data-slide-public-id="6" data-title="Ontbo" class="n2-ss-slide n2-ow  n2-ss-slide-4096"><div role="note" class="n2-ss-slide--focus" tabindex="-1">Ontbo</div><div class="n2-ss-layers-container n2-ss-slide-limiter n2-ow"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-p0dgdn5ZYQ8x" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-0oOwB1LSZkOc" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-0oOwB1LSZkOc-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n2-ss-stretch-layer n-uc-ngMZ4U6f1450" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-ngMZ4U6f1450-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-zaILiYx7Binh" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-zaILiYx7Binh-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-OANPYw4PPIv4" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item31" class="n2-font-cd8573d8a507c95a4dc96d2cf74b8d59-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;"> L’UTC, là où les idées deviennent réalités </div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-xqPRPK25BoMS" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d59dca73119e9ed568f3684d94eea568-paragraph   ">Saviez-vous qu’ONTBO, une startup spécialisée dans l’intelligence artificielle émotionnelle, est née à l’UTC ? Fondée par Athénaïs Oslati, diplômée de l’UTC, ONTBO développe une IA capable de comprendre nos émotions en temps réel grâce à l’analyse des expressions du visage, de la voix, des mots utilisés ou encore des signaux cérébraux. Objectif : rendre les interactions homme-machine plus naturelles, plus humaines et plus efficaces ! Une belle illustration de la façon dont l’innovation technologique peut être pensée pour répondre aux besoins concrets de la société.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-G3h3auI9cF7k n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-click="n2ss.trigger(e.currentTarget, 'details');" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-button-container n2-ss-item-content n2-ow n2-font-b6843e460493f4d2e4f47b6d9745514d-link  n2-ss-nowrap n2-ss-button-container--non-full-width"><a class="n2-style-c6c5507bd4502a08633174b84f534e5b-heading  n2-ow " target="_blank" href="https://youtu.be/noM7V7wMP3I?feature=shared"><div><div>Voir la vidéo</div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-POIh4JH5hPFR" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-POIh4JH5hPFR-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-Fxn39RGzo8lr" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item34" class="n2_ss_video_player n2-ss-item-content n2-ow-all" data-aspect-ratio="16:9"><div class="n2_ss_video_player__placeholder" ></div><div id="n2-ss-851item34-frame"></div><div class="n2_ss_video_player__cover" data-force-pointer=""><picture class="n2-ow-all skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><source srcset="//www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/slider/cache/fcd3c0c24aa0fa0e7105b15e92f76ed3/hqdefault.webp" type="image/webp" media="(max-width: 200px)" class="skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><source srcset="//www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/slider/cache/cb63b3c5b541b8cee7e5b814a3abb142/hqdefault.webp" type="image/webp" class="skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><img class="n2_ss_video_cover skip-lazy" alt="Lecture" loading="lazy" width="480" height="360" data-skip-lazy="1" src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/noM7V7wMP3I/hqdefault.jpg" /></picture><img class="n2_ss_video_play_btn skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1" width="48" height="48" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Play"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-CwYGp5IhFSzP" data-pm="normal" data-hided