</div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-0JZRlfSI0Ckh n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-click="n2ss.trigger(e.currentTarget, 'details');" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-button-container n2-ss-item-content n2-ow n2-font-b6843e460493f4d2e4f47b6d9745514d-link  n2-ss-nowrap n2-ss-button-container--non-full-width"><a class="n2-style-c6c5507bd4502a08633174b84f534e5b-heading  n2-ow " target="_blank" href="https://interactions.utc.fr/thematiques/international/40-ans-de-partenariat-avec-le-bresil/"><div><div>En savoir plus</div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-xzSQdBQUOZ8J" data-pm="normal" data-hidedesktopportrait="1" data-hidetabletportrait="1" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-xzSQdBQUOZ8J-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-ttDxHfzIgEvu" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-ttDxHfzIgEvu-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-U1eV1kIyw94h" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-U1eV1kIyw94h-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-yBJVl9odP6lZ" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-yBJVl9odP6lZ-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-PyMY9WxOSnHS n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item77" class="n2-font-321dc5071321283da51868cafdcfd437-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:inline-block;">Impression moléculaire : une technologie de pointe</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-RN92QDdjlQsN" data-pm="default" role="button" onclick="n2ss.applyActionWithClick(event, 'next');" data-href="#" tabindex="0" data-force-pointer="" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-RN92QDdjlQsN-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-mWTJVcrb71VR n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><span class="n2i  n2-ss-851item78 nfa nfa-long-arrow-right n2-ss-item-content" style="font-size:156.25%;"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-slide-duration="0" data-id="3333" data-slide-public-id="14" data-title="nouveau parcours" class="n2-ss-slide n2-ow  n2-ss-slide-3333"><div role="note" class="n2-ss-slide--focus" tabindex="-1">nouveau parcours</div><div class="n2-ss-layers-container n2-ss-slide-limiter n2-ow"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-OzgWALpU7eYD" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-wehurFoMHY4z" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-wehurFoMHY4z-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n2-ss-stretch-layer n-uc-TEjoeFk0alSK" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-TEjoeFk0alSK-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-1mAjv4TLZ2PI" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-1mAjv4TLZ2PI-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-QUZ9Ib2Pa0m8 n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item79" class="n2-font-a0801e962196f92af10770cb13115e64-hover n2-style-586043f04afba270c9d0bd72659a1aef-heading   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:inline-block;">FORMATION</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-ZHWOHb6VLsCR" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item80" class="n2-font-cd8573d8a507c95a4dc96d2cf74b8d59-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">Un nouveau parcours pour le master Humanités et Industries Créatives</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-IVPS6CA392fh" data-pm="normal" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d59dca73119e9ed568f3684d94eea568-paragraph   ">Dès septembre, l’UTC proposera un nouveau parcours intitulé « Conception, Usages et Recherche Technologique » au sein de la mention Humanités et Industries Créatives. À partir de la rentrée 2025, une première promotion d’une quinzaine d’étudiants va se former aux problématiques liées aux interactions entre l’humain et son milieu naturel, social et technique.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-5C3V9Rn5cOWY n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-click="n2ss.trigger(e.currentTarget, 'details');" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-button-container n2-ss-item-content n2-ow n2-font-b6843e460493f4d2e4f47b6d9745514d-link  n2-ss-nowrap n2-ss-button-container--non-full-width"><a class="n2-style-c6c5507bd4502a08633174b84f534e5b-heading  n2-ow " target="_blank" href="https://interactions.utc.fr/thematiques/technologie-et-sciences-de-l-homme/un-nouveau-parcours-pour-le-master-humanites-et-industries-creatives/"><div><div>En savoir plus</div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-vYKvE8KZzle9" data-pm="normal" data-hidedesktopportrait="1" data-hidetabletportrait="1" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-vYKvE8KZzle9-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-oCxonCWqVkw7" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-oCxonCWqVkw7-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-42tTQMfeZsvG" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-42tTQMfeZsvG-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-iQvyQdIgptc7" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-iQvyQdIgptc7-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-YfaMrWYdlw0c n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item83" class="n2-font-321dc5071321283da51868cafdcfd437-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:inline-block;">Signature d’un accord de double diplôme avec l’Université Française d’Egypte (UFE)</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-o8fJA3Kxy2Ls" data-pm="default" role="button" onclick="n2ss.applyActionWithClick(event, 'next');" data-href="#" tabindex="0" data-force-pointer="" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-o8fJA3Kxy2Ls-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-QPHyzjOr6Bnz n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><span class="n2i  n2-ss-851item84 nfa nfa-long-arrow-right n2-ss-item-content" style="font-size:156.25%;"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-slide-duration="0" data-id="4095" data-slide-public-id="15" data-title="AtmosGear" class="n2-ss-slide n2-ow  n2-ss-slide-4095"><div role="note" class="n2-ss-slide--focus" tabindex="-1">AtmosGear</div><div class="n2-ss-layers-container n2-ss-slide-limiter n2-ow"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-EI5Nvou6exwv" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-6E1WWbC7bSqf" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-6E1WWbC7bSqf-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n2-ss-stretch-layer n-uc-mTOdWMwA4dI9" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-mTOdWMwA4dI9-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-i10d4aWFsmg1" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-i10d4aWFsmg1-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-kDhs58CaUDac" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item85" class="n2-font-cd8573d8a507c95a4dc96d2cf74b8d59-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;"> L’UTC, là où les idées deviennent réalités </div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-IWnXLATeaW65" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d59dca73119e9ed568f3684d94eea568-paragraph   ">Saviez-vous qu’AtmosGear, la startup qui a lancé les premiers rollers électriques au monde, est née à l’UTC ? Fondée par Mido Soliman, diplômé de l’UTC, et avec l’aide de Stanislas Raba, Chief Technology Officer, AtmosGear révolutionne notre mobilité urbaine avec une solution à la fois innovante, ludique et durable ! Un exemple inspirant de la façon dont les rêves d’enfants deviennent des projets étudiants, puis des innovations concrètes accessibles à chacun !</p>
</div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-3QKcXMplSIwl n2-ss-layer--auto" data-pm="normal" data-click="n2ss.trigger(e.currentTarget, 'details');" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-button-container n2-ss-item-content n2-ow n2-font-b6843e460493f4d2e4f47b6d9745514d-link  n2-ss-nowrap n2-ss-button-container--non-full-width"><a class="n2-style-c6c5507bd4502a08633174b84f534e5b-heading  n2-ow " target="_blank" href="https://youtu.be/MWZqwmRsySg?feature=shared"><div><div>Voir la vidéo</div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-cb7gmeD9CHTR" data-pm="default" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-cb7gmeD9CHTR-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-Kxvo3GSL40f4" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-851item88" class="n2_ss_video_player n2-ss-item-content n2-ow-all" data-aspect-ratio="16:9"><div class="n2_ss_video_player__placeholder" ></div><div id="n2-ss-851item88-frame"></div><div class="n2_ss_video_player__cover" data-force-pointer=""><picture class="n2-ow-all skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><source srcset="//www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/slider/cache/1089a166e9e7009f31264d9677dff724/hqdefault.webp" type="image/webp" media="(max-width: 200px)" class="skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><source srcset="//www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/slider/cache/c5abd2b115d2eb44b39bd4a8458e8053/hqdefault.webp" type="image/webp" class="skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1"><img class="n2_ss_video_cover skip-lazy" alt="Lecture" loading="lazy" width="480" height="360" data-skip-lazy="1" src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MWZqwmRsySg/hqdefault.jpg" /></picture><img class="n2_ss_video_play_btn skip-lazy" data-skip-lazy="1" width="48" height="48" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Play"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-38ar4c9Zv7gi" data-pm="normal" data-hided