<a id="link_button-4337-35681" class="ct-link-button" href="https://www.utc.fr/utc/actualites/breves/" target="_blank"  >Plus de brèves</a></div><div id="div_block-4301-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-4339-35681" class="ct-text-block" >Avec son offre de formation, l'UTC donne à chaque étudiant&nbsp; l’opportunité de construire son parcours pédagogique en adéquation avec ses ambitions professionnelles.<br></div><div id="div_block-5606-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-5602-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-5603-35681" class="ct-text-block" >5<br></div><div id="text_block-5605-35681" class="ct-text-block" >spécialités&nbsp;<br>ingénieurs<br></div></div><div id="div_block-5609-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-5610-35681" class="ct-text-block" >5<br></div><div id="text_block-5611-35681" class="ct-text-block" >mentions<br>de master<br></div></div><div id="div_block-5613-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-5614-35681" class="ct-text-block" >1</div><div id="text_block-5615-35681" class="ct-text-block" >bachelor&nbsp;<br>UTC/EDHEC&nbsp;&nbsp;</div></div><div id="div_block-5616-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-5617-35681" class="ct-text-block" >1</div><div id="text_block-5618-35681" class="ct-text-block" >licence<br>professionnelle</div></div></div><div id="div_block-6160-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-6164-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-6165-35681" class="ct-text-block" >5</div><div id="text_block-6166-35681" class="ct-text-block" >mastères<br>spécialisés®</div></div><div id="div_block-6167-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-6168-35681" class="ct-text-block" >8</div><div id="text_block-6169-35681" class="ct-text-block" >laboratoires<br>de recherche</div></div><div id="div_block-6170-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-6171-35681" class="ct-text-block" >1</div><div id="text_block-6172-35681" class="ct-text-block" >école<br>doctorale</div></div><div id="div_block-6161-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-6162-35681" class="ct-text-block" >1</div><div id="text_block-6163-35681" class="ct-text-block" >centre<br>d'innovation</div></div></div><a id="link_button-4344-35681" class="ct-link-button" href="https://www.utc.fr/formations/candidater-a-lutc/"   >CANDIDATER</a></div></div></div></section><section id="section-6260-35681" class=" ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"></div></section><section id="section-6261-35681" class=" ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-6262-35681" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-6263-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-6264-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="fancy_icon-6265-35681" class="ct-fancy-icon" ><svg id="svg-fancy_icon-6265-35681"><use xlink:href="#Lineariconsicon-users"></use></svg></div><h2 id="headline-6266-35681" class="ct-headline">Votre profil</h2></div><div id="code_block-6267-35681" class="ct-code-block" ></div><div id="_toggle-6268-35681" class="oxy-toggle t-auto-close"  data-oxy-toggle-initial-state="closed" data-oxy-toggle-active-class="toggle-4052-expanded" >
