</div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-5975-35681" class=" ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-5976-35681" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-5981-35681" class="ct-div-block" ></div><div id="div_block-5977-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-5978-35681" class="ct-text-block" >À la fois université et école d'ingénieurs, l'UTC est construite sur une pédagogie de l'autonomie et une recherche technologique interdisciplinaire orientée vers l'innovation.<br></div><div id="text_block-5979-35681" class="ct-text-block" >L'UTC forme des ingénieurs, masters et docteurs aptes à appréhender les interactions de la technologie avec l'homme et la société.<br></div><a id="link_button-5980-35681" class="ct-link-button" href="https://www.utc.fr/utc/lutc-en-bref/"   >En savoir plus sur l'UTC</a></div></div></div></section><section id="section-2874-35681" class=" ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-2875-35681" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-2876-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-3687-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><img  id="image-3688-35681" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2022/06/divers18.jpg" class="ct-image img-hover"/><img  id="image-4831-35681" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2022/06/divers17.jpg" class="ct-image img-hover"/><img  id="image-4829-35681" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2022/06/divers20.jpg" class="ct-image img-hover"/><img  id="image-3689-35681" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2022/06/divers19.jpg" class="ct-image img-hover"/><img  id="image-4832-35681" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2022/06/divers22.jpg" class="ct-image img-hover"/><img  id="image-4830-35681" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2022/06/divers21.jpg" class="ct-image img-hover"/></div></div><div id="div_block-2885-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="div_block-3135-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="fancy_icon-3136-35681" class="ct-fancy-icon" ><svg id="svg-fancy_icon-3136-35681"><use xlink:href="#FontAwesomeicon-calendar"></use></svg></div><h2 id="headline-3137-35681" class="ct-headline">AGENDA</h2></div><div id="_dynamic_list-2982-35681" class="oxy-dynamic-list"><div id="div_block-2983-35681-1" class="ct-div-block" data-id="div_block-2983-35681"><img id="image-2984-35681-1" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2025/09/semainerose.jpg" class="ct-image" data-id="image-2984-35681"><div id="div_block-3109-35681-1" class="ct-div-block" data-id="div_block-3109-35681"><div id="text_block-2752-35681-1" class="ct-text-block" data-id="text_block-2752-35681"><span id="span-2753-35681-1" class="ct-span" data-id="span-2753-35681">12 au 17 OCTOBRE 2025</span><br></div><h3 id="headline-2985-35681-1" class="ct-headline" data-id="headline-2985-35681"><span id="span-2986-35681-1" class="ct-span" data-id="span-2986-35681"><a href="https://www.utc.fr/agenda-actualites/la-semaine-rose/">La semaine rose</a></span></h3></div></div><div id="div_block-2983-35681-2" class="ct-div-block" data-id="div_block-2983-35681"><img id="image-2984-35681-2" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2025/06/t3.jpg" class="ct-image" data-id="image-2984-35681"><div id="div_block-3109-35681-2" class="ct-div-block" data-id="div_block-3109-35681"><div id="text_block-2752-35681-2" class="ct-text-block" data-id="text_block-2752-35681"><span id="span-2753-35681-2" class="ct-span" data-id="span-2753-35681">15-16 OCTOBRE 2025</span><br></div><h3 id="headline-2985-35681-2" class="ct-headline" data-id="headline-2985-35681"><span id="span-2986-35681-2" class="ct-span" data-id="span-2986-35681"><a href="https://www.utc.fr/agenda-actualites/colloque-ts3-technological-systems-sustainability-and-safety/">Colloque TS3 &ldquo;Technological Systems, Sustainability and Safety&rdquo;</a></span></h3></div></div><div id="div_block-2983-35681-3" class="ct-div-block" data-id="div_block-2983-35681"><img id="image-2984-35681-3" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2025/09/comutech25.jpg" class="ct-image" data-id="image-2984-35681"><div id="div_block-3109-35681-3" class="ct-div-block" data-id="div_block-3109-35681"><div id="text_block-2752-35681-3" class="ct-text-block" data-id="text_block-2752-35681"><span id="span-2753-35681-3" class="ct-span" data-id="span-2753-35681">16 OCTOBRE 2025</span><br></div><h3 id="headline-2985-35681-3" class="ct-headline" data-id="headline-2985-35681"><span id="span-2986-35681-3" class="ct-span" data-id="span-2986-35681"><a href="https://www.utc.fr/agenda-actualites/31e-edition-du-forum-comutec/">31<sup class="ordinal">e</sup> &eacute;dition du Forum Comutec</a></span></h3></div></div><div id="div_block-2983-35681-4" class="ct-div-block" data-id="div_block-2983-35681"><img id="image-2984-35681-4" alt="" src="https://www.utc.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2021/09/prbvl.jpg" class="ct-image" data-id="image-2984-35681"><div id="div_block-3109-35681-4" class="ct-div-block" data-id="div_block-3109-35681"><div id="text_block-2752-35681-4" class="ct-text-block" data-id="text_block-2752-35681"><span id="span-2753-35681-4" class="ct-span" data-id="span-2753-35681">22 NOVEMBRE 2025</span><br></div><h3 id="headline-2985-35681-4" class="ct-headline" data-id="headline-2985-35681"><span id="span-2986-35681-4" class="ct-span" data-id="span-2986-35681"><a href="https://www.utc.fr/agenda-actualites/ceremonie-de-la-38e-edition-du-prix-roberval/">C&eacute;r&eacute;monie de la 38<sup class="ordinal">e</sup> &eacute;dition du Prix Roberval</a></span></h3></div></div>                    
                                            
                                        <div class="oxy-repeater-pages-wrap">
                        <div class="oxy-repeater-pages">
                            <span aria-current="page" class="page-numbers current">1</span>
<a class="page-numbers" href="https://www.utc.fr/page/2/">2</a>
<a class="next page-numbers" href="https://www.utc.fr/page/2/">Suivant&nbsp;&raquo;</a>                        </div>
                    </div>
                                        
                    </div>
<a id="link_button-2987-35681" class="ct-link-button" href="https://www.utc.fr/utc/actualites/agenda/" target="_blank"  >Plus d'événements</a></div></div></div></section><section id="section-4845-35681" class=" ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="new_columns-4846-35681" class="ct-new-columns" ><div id="div_block-4848-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="text_block-4849-35681" class="ct-text-block" >Créer des partenariats sur le long terme avec les entreprises, transformer la taxe d'apprentissage en investissement…&nbsp;<br></div><div id="text_block-4858-35681" class="ct-text-block" >L'UTC s'est dotée, pour soutenir l'ensemble de sa politique de partenariat, d'outils et de structures spécifiques, qui favorisent l'émergence d'une relation université / entreprise fiable, de confiance et durable sur le plan des ressources humaines comme sur celui de la recherche partenariale.<br></div><a id="link_button-4885-35681" class="ct-link-button" href="https://www.utc.fr/innovation/partenariat-campus-entreprise/"   >En savoir plus sur les partenariats</a></div><div id="div_block-4847-35681" class="ct-div-block" ></div></div></div></section><section id="section-2598-35681" class=" ct-section" ><div class="ct-section-inner-wrap"><div id="div_block-3410-35681" class="ct-div-block" ><div id="fancy_icon-3411-35681" class="ct-fancy-icon" ><svg id="svg-fancy_icon-3411-35681"><use xlink:href="#Lineariconsicon-camera-video"></use></svg></div><h2 id="headline-3412-35681" class="ct-headline">DERNIÈRES VIDÉOS</h2></div><div id="shortcode-2600-35681" class="ct-shortcode" ><div class="n2-section-smartslider fitvidsignore  n2_clear" data-ssid="853"><div id="n2-ss-853-align" class="n2-ss-align"><div class="n2-padding"><div id="n2-ss-853" data-creator="Smart Slider 3" data-responsive="fullwidth" class="n2-ss-slider n2-ow n2-has-hover n2notransition   n2-ss-showcase-horizontal">



