 n2-ow n-uc-36FJrRUJQ3jV" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-p2neh2ngm7xn" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-p2neh2ngm7xn-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-8e1Y2bgwDRnl" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-8e1Y2bgwDRnl-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-J4QRGeUJfIRi" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-J4QRGeUJfIRi-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-eRNVWXRv7jzL" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-859item64" class="n2-font-bb8a8ebbef82965b045c7cc66415e973-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">Céline Anciaux</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-9OJ546s7f9gm" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;delay&quot;:0.05,&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-859item65" class="n2-font-53800138ef911fbb422d999cedf39f67-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">Femmes dirigeantes, dans le BTP aussi !</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-1cvybXKXL0vI" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;delay&quot;:0.15,&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d90a9b84626b12a176d70e24355b0ebb-paragraph   ">Comment une entreprise comme Brezillon s’empare-t-elle de la question de l’égalité femme-homme ? Le monde du BTP avait déjà commencé sa transformation depuis plusieurs années, mais la société avance et le BTP doit continuer a évoluer. Vision de l’intérieur avec le témoignage de Céline Anciaux, responsable du développement commercial chez Brezillon. </p>
