<div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-H7G6RFaG8NFn" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-9BXWqS3lx1fl" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-9BXWqS3lx1fl-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-MCm4Oul33Wd2" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-MCm4Oul33Wd2-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-pg3MhRaU0617" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-pg3MhRaU0617-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-VHr2YvsNzctb" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-859item183" class="n2-font-bb8a8ebbef82965b045c7cc66415e973-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">Jean-Louis Chaussade</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-f3wTUjYRYzbx" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;delay&quot;:0.05,&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-859item184" class="n2-font-53800138ef911fbb422d999cedf39f67-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">Élargir mon horizon<br></div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-VpYzSDi2dM2r" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;delay&quot;:0.15,&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d90a9b84626b12a176d70e24355b0ebb-paragraph   ">D’abord directeur général pendant 15 ans, Jean-Louis Chaussade devient, en 2019, président de Suez. Coopté en 2016 par le conseil d’administration de l’UTC, il en prend, dans la foulée, la présidence. Un mandat qui a été renouvelé en décembre 2021 pour une durée de 4 ans. </p>
