r n2-ow n-uc-N5acjQRAkUeH" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-NHDnX8GFQS8D" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-NHDnX8GFQS8D-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-ZFt0xMeDhAK8" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-ZFt0xMeDhAK8-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-EwSKSnf1X9Uz" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-EwSKSnf1X9Uz-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-BGD0gxvkgCTT" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-859item190" class="n2-font-bb8a8ebbef82965b045c7cc66415e973-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">Laurent Forny</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-dL3wfwYGH5V0" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;delay&quot;:0.05,&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-859item191" class="n2-font-53800138ef911fbb422d999cedf39f67-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">L’esprit d’équipe</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-smVkB5L2JeQv" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;delay&quot;:0.15,&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d90a9b84626b12a176d70e24355b0ebb-paragraph   ">Diplômé de l’UTC en génie des procédés en 2004, Laurent Forny a poursuivi, toujours à l’UTC, par ce qui, à l’époque, s’appelait un DEA (master 2) et une thèse. Il est, depuis 2008, chef de projet chez Nestlé. En 2021, il a parrainé le prix de thèse Guy-Deniélou. Portrait d’un homme à l’esprit d’équipe chevillé au corps. </p>
