2-ow"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-v1xebDTWBfcy" data-sstype="slide" data-pm="default"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-bMnhVAvxECIe" data-pm="default" data-sstype="content" data-hasbackground="0"><div class="n2-ss-section-main-content n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n2-ow n-uc-bMnhVAvxECIe-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n2-ss-layer--block n2-ss-has-self-align n-uc-civaUqNwWT8h" data-pm="normal" data-sstype="row"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row n2-ss-layer-with-background n-uc-civaUqNwWT8h-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer-row-inner "><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-wN6tudDUcFwF" data-pm="default" data-sstype="col"><div class="n2-ss-layer-col n2-ss-layer-with-background n2-ss-layer-content n-uc-wN6tudDUcFwF-inner"><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-iyApwoqTq4nk" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-859item218" class="n2-font-bb8a8ebbef82965b045c7cc66415e973-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">Florent Latrive</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-DU7Rreb5t7Lp" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;delay&quot;:0.05,&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-sstype="layer"><div id="n2-ss-859item219" class="n2-font-53800138ef911fbb422d999cedf39f67-hover   n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow" style="display:block;">La passion pour les médias</div></div><div class="n2-ss-layer n2-ow n-uc-1iUVZVrGlPD6" data-pm="normal" data-animv2="{&quot;basic&quot;:{&quot;in&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;basic&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Bottom fade&quot;,&quot;keyFrames&quot;:[{&quot;delay&quot;:0.15,&quot;opacity&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;-20&quot;}]}}}" data-hidemobileportrait="1" data-sstype="layer"><div class="n2-ss-item-content n2-ss-text n2-ow-all"><div class=""><p class="n2-font-d90a9b84626b12a176d70e24355b0ebb-paragraph   ">Diplômé de l’UTC en génie informatique en 1995, Florent Latrive n’a jamais exercé son métier d’ingénieur. Passionné de presse et des impacts de la technologie sur la société, il est directeur éditorial du numérique à France Culture et maître de conférences associé en journalisme numérique à l’Institut français de presse (Paris II Assas). Portrait d’un homme dont la passion pour les médias lui a fait ouvrir les portes les plus verrouillées.</p>
